claimInBridgeTransfer.t.sol
├── given recovery mode is off
│  ├── when sender is not the Mechanic
│  │  └── it should revert with UnauthorizedCaller
│  └── when sender is the Mechanic
│     ├── it should decrease the corresponding adapter's token balance by amount
│     ├── it should increase the caliber's token balance by amount
│     └── it should emit a InBridgeTransferClaimed event
└── given recovery mode is on
   ├── when sender is not the Security Council
   │  └── it should revert with UnauthorizedCaller
   └── when sender is the Security Council
      ├── it should decrease the corresponding adapter's token balance by amount
      ├── it should increase the caliber's token balance by amount
      └── it should emit a InBridgeTransferClaimed event
